[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "ここがクア州の海辺……\n船がたくさんあって、思ったより賑やかね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "あれ？　ミルカとユリエさんだ！\nおーい！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "シャル……！　どうしてここに……というか、\n大きい声で呼ばないでよ……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "8814674670384979784",
		"text": "ミルカさん、ユリエさん、こんにちは。\nマリオンさんから旅に出たって聞いてますよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "8971561709699782619",
		"text": "ミルカも水遊びに誘おうと思ったのに、\nいなかったからさー",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "水遊びのために、わざわざ二人でクア州まで来たの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "8814674670384979784",
		"text": "えっと、クア州に来たのは――",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "コルテス",
		"romanized_name": "Kortes",
		"model_path_hash": "6745194160365014115",
		"text": "船で海を渡るためなんだ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3797902451650633333",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "あら、コルテス。\nそういえば、クア州は造船が盛んらしいわね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "コルテス",
		"romanized_name": "Kortes",
		"model_path_hash": "6745194160365014115",
		"text": "ああ。船を貸してもらえるっていうから、\nそれを使ってヴィアベル州まで行ってみようと思ってな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3797902451650633333",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "8814674670384979784",
		"text": "ヴィアベル州の海も、とっても綺麗なので\n遊びに行こうって話になって",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "ヴィアベル州……ランターナ王国内の群島ね。\n私たちの次の目的地もそこよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "8971561709699782619",
		"text": "おお！　じゃあ一緒に行こうよ！\nみんなで船に乗って冒険だー！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "いいの？　それならお願いしたいわ。\nミルカも二人に会えて嬉しそうだし",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "姉さん、適当なこと言わないで",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "8814674670384979784",
		"text": "わたしも、みんなで一緒に行けたら嬉しいです！\nコルテス兄さま、いいですか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "コルテス",
		"romanized_name": "Kortes",
		"model_path_hash": "6745194160365014115",
		"text": "ああ、もちろんだ。\nもうすぐ出発するから、荷物をまとめておけよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3797902451650633333",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "ありがとう、みんな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "8814674670384979784",
		"text": "ねぇロッテ、浮き輪は持ってきた？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "8971561709699782619",
		"text": "もちろん！　たくさん船に積んどいたよ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……もしかして、手作り？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "8971561709699782619",
		"text": "うん！　錬金術で作った「一瞬で膨らむ浮き輪」だよ！\n船が沈みそうになっても、それに掴まれば大丈夫！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "コルテス",
		"romanized_name": "Kortes",
		"model_path_hash": "6745194160365014115",
		"text": "冗談でもやめてくれ。\n船が転覆したらシャレにならん",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3797902451650633333",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "コルテス、操縦は任せていいのね？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "コルテス",
		"romanized_name": "Kortes",
		"model_path_hash": "6745194160365014115",
		"text": "任せとけ。\n危険だと思ったら、すぐ引き返す",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3797902451650633333",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "ヴィアベル州の海は、どんな所なの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "コルテス",
		"romanized_name": "Kortes",
		"model_path_hash": "6745194160365014115",
		"text": "水が澄んでて、魚も多い。\n泳ぐにはちょうどいいだろう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3797902451650633333",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "8971561709699782619",
		"text": "あたし、魚掴み取りしたい！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……シャル、また変なこと考えてる",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "8971561709699782619",
		"text": "えー、いいじゃん！　\nみんなで競争しようよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "ふふ。まあ、ケガだけはしないように",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ・エルミナス",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte Elminus",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "明るく快活な錬金術士。ミルカの幼馴染。\n愛称はシャリステラと同じ「シャリー」",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "とある使命を背負った錬金術士。\n愛称はシャルロッテと同じ「シャリー」",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "コルテス",
		"romanized_name": "Kortes",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "船を守る一族の戦士。シャリステラの幼馴染。\n社交的で頭の回転が速く、頼りがいがあるしっかり者",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3797902451650633333",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]